<title>USA: HFNC Financial stake cut by group to 4.6pct.</title>
<headline>HFNC Financial stake cut by group to 4.6pct.</headline>
<dateline>WASHINGTON 1997-04-21</dateline>
<text>
<p>A group including South Carolina investor Jerry Zucker said Monday it has reduced its stake in HFNC Financial Corp to 790,000 common shares or 4.6 percent.</p>
<p>In a filing with the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission, the group said it sold 86,500 shares of the Charlotte, N.C. company in transactions on March 3 and April 11 at prices ranging from $18.75 to $21.50 a share.</p>
